summary:
A path opener with a huge passion for reaching the top. I believe authenticity is the most important. With 5 years of working experience in International business in Food, I pay meticulous attention to detail, always pursue new challenges, and have ambitious career goals.
Currently working as the head of the operation in the fish capital of Holland, Urk. As a pioneer ex-pat in Urk, my linguistics skill enables me to operate any seafood business opportunity between Europe and the USA. My adaptability and European experience turn me into a good associator between East and West cultures. Should you have any questions, I will assist with your request with my utmost professionalism and passion.

lindylin35@gmail.com
